From the income statement:

- Total Revenue = $775,598.77

Gross Profit Margin = Gross Profit / Total Revenue
Gross Profit Margin = $279,378.77 / $775,598.77 = 0.36020 (rounded to 5 decimal places)

Step 2: Convert to percentage
